channel.description:
[s]1) I've forgotten how to edit the shop price...can you tell me which file and part it is that I edit? And secondly, how do I make it so that I can type in the EXACT price I want instead of doing all that other stuff, if it's possible? (If not, can you tell me what I have to do to the price? rofl)[/s]
2) How do you make the superman command? You know, the one where you character appears to be flying. Also, please add any cool commands you know. (No item or mod/admin commands, please. :))
Thanks in advance! ;o
Off-topic, i'm currently looking for mods, admins, and a co-owner to my beta server...I'm currently accepting testers to my server.. Please reply if you're interesting in contributing your ideas and suggestions! xD
